<HTML><HEAD><META NAME="Description" CONTENT="The venerable guild Forgotten Truth, Everquest, expands to Asheron's Call"><META NAME="Keywords" CONTENT="message boards, forum, free forums, free message boards, visual basic, programming, programmers, community, vb, directx, games, dx, basic, bulletin boards, online communities, discussion forums, The, Forgotten, Truth, In, Asheron's, Call"><TITLE>Overlord quest. - www.ezboard.com</TITLE></HEAD><BODY TEXT=#ffffff BGCOLOR=#000000 LINK=#70db93 VLINK=#00ff00 ALINK=#FF0000><CENTER><CENTER><a href="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/cscintro.html" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.ezboard.com/banners/cscuserbanner.gif"></a></CENTER><BR><TABLE WIDTH=95%><TR><TD><B><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/bforgottentruthforeignlegion><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Forgotten Truth Foreign Legion</FONT></A></B><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<B>> <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>General</FONT></A></B><BR><B>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<B>> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Overlord quest.</FONT></B></TD><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddTopicScreenFromWeb><IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/newTopic1.gif border=0></A>&nbsp; &nbsp; <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=520.topic><IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/addReply1.gif border=0></A></TD></TR><TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT></TD><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showMessage?topicID=516.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1><< Prev Topic</FONT></A> &nbsp;<A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showMessage?topicID=518.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Next Topic >></FONT></A> </TD></TR></TABLE><table border=0 width=95% cellpadding=5 cellspacing=1><TR><TD valign=top><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#000000>Author</FONT><B></TD><TD valign=top><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#000000>Comment</FONT><B></FONT></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#2f2f4f><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Crow</FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Unregistered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>3/4/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>3:25:56 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=520.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Reply</FONT></A></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Overlord quest.</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Hey all. Well, we did it. The Overlord was slain several times. My only regret was dieing before my chance at a pull on his uber chest ... but at least everyone else got what they came for. I might have lost all my high dollar death items, but having Rayna by my side as we two stood our ground and held that gate was a sight to behold! I have no idea how many tumerocks we killed by full frontal assualt or by sniping them from the towers and walls of the fort, but rest assured I went through a hundred arrows while Dia and Roy made their way back to the fort!<br>
<br>
Now, since I'll be gone for about a week I'm going to leave you with a little puzzle to figure out. Tonight, or should I say this morning, Rav was the first FTFL member to successfuly cast the spell Recall Sanctuary!!! The place looks pretty cool but I didn't go exploring to far. Lets see who else can cast the spell by the time I get back. Buff your item to 200+ and try this formula: Copper Scarab - Brown Taper - Comfrey - Random Taper - Orange Taper - Cobalt - Random Taper - Rowan. That's it...no powder in this one. Rav's 2 random tapers were both grey but I'm sure everyone's will be an assortment of colors. The only way to do it is to brute force the combos. Now, one word of caution..there is a bug that when you teleport you are stuck in War Mode and have to log off and on again to work normally. BUT --- before you log off look at your spell and write down the combo!!!! For some reason this spell does NOT load on your spell book and the only way to cast it again is to write it down and do the spell test thing again.<br>
<br>
Anyway...good luck casting. When I get back I'm going to have to hunt for awhile to make enough cash for 3 new death item master robes before I can go questing again. However...I think the sparking stone should be our next target.<br>
<br>
Cya.</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#6B8E23><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/bforgottentruthforeignlegion.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=dia>Dia</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_thatch.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>3/4/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>11:55:57 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=520.topic&index=1><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Reply</FONT></A></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Thanks to you all!</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">This has been a wonderfull night; extreme fighting like I like it. Adrenaline was running in my bloodstrem for 3 hours in a row. My regret is that Wamba, our best reporter, was not there to write all the story.<br>
<br>
I hope this was not to hard on you. I know you had to die often to give me that thrill, and I thank you for it. Being there was the nicest gift you could offer me, better than any equippement.<br>
<br>
A mention of courage and survival instinct must be awarded to Rayna. She made it all the way without a single death. She really knows how to please the cook! (by eating all her soup like a big girl!)<br>
<br>
I will work on this recall sanctuary spell. I will also tie to the black dominion. It will get us closer to the sparking vault and we will be able to get a new mask for Roy and Crow.<br>
<br>
May there be many more of these hunts!</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#2f2f4f><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Crow</FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Unregistered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>3/4/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>1:36:19 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=520.topic&index=2><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Reply</FONT></A></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Notes on Recall Sanctuary</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">I just logged on for a few minutes and had Crow try to cast this spell. He has the same tapers as Raven for the random ones. Not sure if they really are random at all or if the random tapers are the same for all characters on an account. Anyway, Crow made it with this formula: Copper Scarab - Brown Taper - Comfrey - Grey Random Taper - Orange Taper - Cobalt - Grey Random Taper - Rowan.</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#6B8E23><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/ukrystl.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Krystl</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_star.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>3/5/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>12:05:15 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=520.topic&index=3><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Reply</FONT></A></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Overlord quest.</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Saturday night was the best fun I've had in AC in months!  It had everything a girl could want.  Action, loot, allies, enemies.  I think the most heart stopping moment for me was once we were inside the fort - we moved all the way over the the stairs, but with about 20 tumeroks pounding us, I didn't know where to go, I tried climbing the ladder when I got down to less than 10hp, and that's when I had just the instant I needed to eat my soup!  I hadn't had dinner, and it was quite tasty!  My compliments to the chef Dia! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Actually, I was saved more than once by drinking up that soup, but, also, I must admit...there is a good reason why I did not die.  I hid behind the three of you, of course! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :eek --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/eek.gif ALT=":eek"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Celeroy sacrificed himself more than once, and Crow did the big save in the end, leaving the three of us safe at the Overlord spot.  Crow gives me more credit than due - honestly, while he buffed, I only had to pick off a few warriors and priests, nothing high or very hard <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   But...I did have lots of fun helping him hold that gate!  At first, I was reluctant, thinking...we're going to let Dia leave, and shut the gate with just the two of us inside??  But, of course, it was the PERFECT plan, and it proved to be most efficient, and fun!<br>
<br>
Thank you all!  I had SO much fun!  A special thanks to my brother and patron for the fur coat.  Ok...I may love the kitties, but I cannot hold onto my activist ways.  Once I donned that coat, it was all over for me.  Just someone TRY to rip it off me now! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Dia, I missed Wamba too, we really could have used him to throw out in front of us to distract the monsters while we all ran for the uber loot!!  I could have used some of his chocolate too...&lt;drools&gt;<br>
<br>
&lt;special message to Wamba....if you ever decide to come back, I'll let you engrave my shirt this time <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> &gt;<br>
<br>
Rayna <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> </font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#2f2f4f><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/ugharadin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gharadin</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>3/5/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#5F9EA0>7:21:08 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=520.topic&index=4><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Reply</FONT></A></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Overlord quest.</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Wow, congratulations everyone!!! The Overlord, that's quite an achievement!</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR></TABLE><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=95%><TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT></TD><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showMessage?topicID=516.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1><< Prev Topic</FONT></A> &nbsp;<A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showMessage?topicID=518.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Next Topic >></FONT></A> </TD></TR></TABLE><BR><TABLE WIDTH=95% BORDER=0><TR><TD><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=520.topic&index=4><IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/addReply1.gif border=0></A></TD><TD><A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.emailToFriend?topicID=520.topic><IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/images/email.gif BORDER=0 ALT="Email This To 